# AI API Configuration
# Choose one of the following providers:

# 1. For OpenAI (AI Mini Tools + DALL-E Thumbnail):
# AI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
# AI_PROVIDER=openai

# 2. For Google Gemini (AI Mini Tools + Enhanced Thumbnail):
# AI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here
# AI_PROVIDER=gemini

# 3. Mock mode (for development without API key):
# AI_PROVIDER=mock

# Note:
# - Gemini: Uses AI to enhance thumbnail design (SVG-based, faster)
# - OpenAI: Uses DALL-E for photorealistic thumbnails (slower, costs more)
# - Mock: Basic SVG thumbnails without AI enhancement
